{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c18ce69d-25b5-44e2-b2c5-71c1e77ba430","content":"Here's the recommended MSTest setup:\n\n## 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`) — minimal with MSTest.Sdk\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` brings in the test framework, runner, and Microsoft.Testing.Platform automatically. No package references needed.\n\n## 2. Enable parallel execution (`.runsettings` or assembly attribute)\n\nAdd a file `testconfig.cs` at the project root:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[assembly: Parallelize(Scope = ExecutionScope.MethodLevel)]\n```\n\nThis runs all test methods in parallel by default.\n\n## 3. Sequential database tests — use `[DoNotParallelize]`\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Insert_CreatesRecord()\n    {\n        // ...\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Delete_RemovesRecord()\n    {\n        // ...\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThe `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute on the class ensures all tests in it run sequentially and never overlap with other parallelized tests.\n\n---\n\n**Summary:**\n\n| Concern | Mechanism |\n|---------|-----------|\n| Minimal project | `MSTest.Sdk/3.8` (no explicit package refs) |\n| Parallel by default | `[assembly: Parallelize(Scope = ExecutionScope.MethodLevel)]` |\n| Sequential DB tests | `[DoNotParallelize]` on the test class |\n\n`ExecutionScope.MethodLevel` gives maximum parallelism (methods across all classes run concurrently). Use `ClassLevel` instead if you want classes to run in parallel but methods within a class to be sequential.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f6301241-9184-4a7a-b2d6-2b63d0bf7718","outputTokens":492,"requestId":"E442:29262A:347E27F:39FABEE:6A02FC0D"},"id":"f93a352b-1599-449c-83f3-061ebec913b7","timestamp":"2026-05-12T10:08:29.660Z","parentId":"c6920001-09c6-4a47-9369-b06f9136d5a0"}
